{"id": 650, "genre": 1001, "title": "你用手机拍照遇到了什么困难？", "description": "拍太丑，女朋友揍了我一顿。", "record_count": 5474, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183500WXBVINdH0ES4CloJ.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-23T12:47:56Z", "options": [{"id": 28160, "content": "拍特写手在抖，拍全景手还是在抖，冬天手机残了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 316752}, {"id": 33025, "content": "怎么自拍嘴都是歪的，以前的山寨机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347847}, {"id": 83202, "content": "utVAs6  <a href=\"http://ofcftvwsaoks.com/\">ofcftvwsaoks</a>, [url=http://dilkhlyfvbuk.com/]dilkhlyfvbuk[/url], [link=http://endzdmyauufu.com/]endzdmyauufu[/link], http://fjyrbfgrkc", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 38914, "content": "手机太大，辛苦拍的造型，发现一只爪子，按不了键", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403499}, {"id": 30724, "content": "照相只是其次,后期各种ps,滤镜才是重点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335706}, {"id": 28165, "content": "调不好焦", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 322959}, {"id": 28166, "content": "拍完照一天都想着怎么p图", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278963}, {"id": 28167, "content": "太清楚，把刚长的颗粒拍出来了，忧伤，p图手艺又不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285820}, {"id": 28170, "content": "放大就算渣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323010}, {"id": 34058, "content": "前置太近，后置太远，脸大景远。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268211}, {"id": 28171, "content": "拍ྉ\u001a\u001a出ྉ\u001a\u001a來ྉ\u001a\u001a不ྉ\u001a\u001a太ྉ\u001a\u001a專ྉ\u001a\u001a業ྉ\u001a\u001a不ྉ\u001a\u001a太ྉ\u001a\u001a好ྉ\u001a\u001a看ྉ\u001a\u001a會ྉ\u001a\u001a被ྉ\u001a\u001a歧ྉ\u001a\u001a視ྉ\u001a\u001a", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 243919}, {"id": 28684, "content": "地铁偷拍被仇视", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326231}, {"id": 28173, "content": "看的时候一种感觉，拍照的时候另一种感觉，但是都不坏，虽然手机的像素没有那么好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323046}, {"id": 31246, "content": "再美的风景自拍也只有大脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334825}, {"id": 28943, "content": "拍照的时候总感觉有什么东西在看我?然后就是不敢拍噗哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328007}, {"id": 28176, "content": "是镜头后面的那个人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323059}, {"id": 28435, "content": "前镜像素太低。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232141}, {"id": 28182, "content": "想拍的没能拍出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306825}, {"id": 28185, "content": "为什么胳膊永远不够长", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311407}, {"id": 28186, "content": "拍出来的永远是黑照??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249412}, {"id": 28442, "content": "大小脸！尴尬笑～?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324534}, {"id": 28187, "content": "拍出来的女友 总会被朋友被朋友评论 你怎么没带女友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323215}, {"id": 32028, "content": "不清晰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341970}, {"id": 28446, "content": "逗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324578}, {"id": 30750, "content": "在蒙古国看到国内绝迹的黄羊群，前不见首后不见尾地缓缓过马路，车辆停下来给让路，可是我一拍下来却是几只羊的效果", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335781}, {"id": 28193, "content": "手机照出来没本人好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323254}, {"id": 28197, "content": "VSCO", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305684}, {"id": 28201, "content": "360度全死角？怎么都找不到传说中的361度！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208374}, {"id": 28202, "content": "拍的和看到的就是感觉差距大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323340}, {"id": 28203, "content": "画面中太多多余的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 295366}, {"id": 28459, "content": "镜子里的自己总是要比手机自拍的好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281762}, {"id": 28205, "content": "闪退", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 317283}, {"id": 30509, "content": "没钱买像素好的phone", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 94536}, {"id": 28206, "content": "有时候看到了好东西，拿出手机拍的时候，那个画面就没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252634}, {"id": 28974, "content": "拍的，不上镜。人帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328253}, {"id": 29486, "content": "拍出来比本人丑?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330774}, {"id": 28207, "content": "手机拍的比人眼看的要丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 104470}, {"id": 28208, "content": "看见别人抱着笨重的单反，心里一阵鄙视，优雅的拿出我的手机随手拍！卡擦！", "image": "img/option/option/201606052117427B1rWnGtoFeclYdj.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287085}, {"id": 28209, "content": "心情大好自拍一张，想发到朋友圈调色了很久最后P了一副墨镜上去挡了半个脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163696}, {"id": 30769, "content": "黑暗处燥点太大～照不出单反的感觉…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301412}, {"id": 28210, "content": "拍照的时候声音消不掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277028}, {"id": 28722, "content": "拍到的永远都是缩小版的天空", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099712}, {"id": 28215, "content": "人家拍出来的照片都很有逼格，自己拍的惨不忍睹", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323451}, {"id": 30007, "content": "一群人自拍 总有头挤不进镜头……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333460}, {"id": 28985, "content": "自拍手太短", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328306}, {"id": 40761, "content": "不上镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419663}, {"id": 28986, "content": "像素太高，把人拍的太清楚太真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327086}, {"id": 28489, "content": "对焦慢，夜景睁眼瞎", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 314833}, {"id": 29773, "content": "晚上闪光灯打开拍照，拍完却是黑的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115693}, {"id": 28238, "content": "手机内存不足", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308923}]}